.:: Einstein-puzzle ::.

The people have 5 different hobbies: skydiving, video-games, singing, writing, fishing
House: ranch-style, victorian, craftsman, cottage, futuristic
There 5 different types of food: pear, raspberry, pepper, peas, apple
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: skydivingmaster, dunhill, pall-mall, prince, blend
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: soccer, lacrosse, badminton, skateboarding, skiing
1. the ranch-style house is the person who's hobby is singing
2. the swedish house is the person who's sport is badminton
3. the victorian house is the person eating peas
4. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is writing
5. the person who's hobby is video-games is the person eating raspberry
6. the pall-mall-smoker is the person who's sport is lacrosse
7. the person who's hobby is fishing is the dunhill-smoker
8. the person eating pepper is in the middle
9. the cottage house is on the far left
10. the blend-smoker is on the left or right of the person who's sport is soccer
11. the person who's sport is skiings is on the left or right of the dunhill-smoker
12. the skydivingmaster-smoker is the person eating pear
13. the craftsman house is the prince-smoker
14. the cottage house is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is skydiving
15. the blend-smoker is on the left or right of the person eating apple

.:: Answer ::.
|		|	1	|	2	|	3	|	4	|	5	|
| Hobby		|    fishing	|     skydiving	|      singing	|     video-games	|     writing	|
| House	|   cottage	|    victorian	|    ranch-style	|    craftsman	|    swedish	|
| Sport		|     soccer	|    skiing	|     lacrosse	|     skateboarding	|      badminton	|
| Food	|    apple	|     peas	|     pepper	|    raspberry	|      pear	|
| Cigar		|   dunhill	|    blend	|  pall-mall	|    prince	|   skydivingmaster	|
